comments: Cauley-Stein (GSW) sets the screen on Conley (UTA) and absorbs the contact.

Gobert (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Burks's (GSW) driving shot attempt.
Spellman (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Bogdanovic's (UTA) driving shot attempt.

Cauley-Stein (GSW) and Gobert (UTA) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.

Burks (GSW) legally contests Mitchell's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Mitchell (UTA) makes contact with Robinson III's (GSW) off-arm that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Burks (GSW) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
Burks (GSW) sets the screen on Conley (UTA) and absorbs the contact.

Bowman (GSW) and Mitchell (UTA) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Spellman (GSW) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).

Replay review of the foul called on Gober (UTA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful.  Gobert makes marginal contact with Burks' (GSW) body as he is collapsing his arm and he cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
